        <div class="body">
            <p>We decided that using Zend::exception() is not recommended after all, because it obscures the <strong>LINE</strong> and <strong>FILE</strong> reported for an exception.</p>

<p>It is better to use exceptions in a traditional way, and use other performance solutions such as a bytecode cache if that is important.</p>

